trans-unit.source: Represents an accept-encoding header value.
trans-unit.target: 表示 Acept-Ecoding 标头值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.TransferCodingHeaderValue> class provides support for the Accept-Encoding header as defined in [RFC 2616](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=241642) by the IETF.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.TransferCodingHeaderValue>类提供了支持的 Accept-encoding 标头中定义[RFC 2616](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=241642)由 IETF。

trans-unit.source: A hash code for the current object.
trans-unit.target: 当前对象的哈希代码。

trans-unit.source: A hash code is a numeric value that is used to identify an object during equality testing.
trans-unit.target: 哈希代码是一个数字值，用于标识相等测试过程中的对象。

trans-unit.source: It can also serve as an index for an object in a collection.
trans-unit.target: 它还可以充当集合中的对象的索引。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.TransferCodingHeaderValue.GetHashCode%2A> method is suitable for use in hashing algorithms and data structures such as a hash table.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.TransferCodingHeaderValue.GetHashCode%2A>方法是适合在哈希算法和数据结构，如哈希表中使用。
